alwaysApply: false
---

# Vitest + RTL Rules

## Queries

- Prefer `getByRole`, `getByLabelText`, `getByText`
- Minimize `getByTestId`

## Interactions

- Use `userEvent` (click, type, etc.)

## Structure

```ts
describe("Component", () => {
  describe("Rendering", () => { ... });
  describe("Props", () => { ... });
  describe("HTML Attributes", () => { ... });
});
```

## ThemeProvider

- Wrap with `ThemeProvider` when testing theme-dependent behavior
